text: Jaime Errázuriz (born 3 August 1923) was a Chilean alpine skier. He competed at the 1948 Winter Olympics and the 1952 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Chilean male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Chile Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Alpine skiers at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:People from Talca Province
